<!--
  Centralized user-facing strings for the whole app.

  Naming conventions:
    common_*          — shared across screens (button labels, placeholders)
    cd_*              — accessibility / contentDescription labels
    action_*          — short imperative buttons (e.g., "Save", "Delete")
    <screen>_*        — screen-scoped copy (settings_*, runner_*, sound_settings_*, …)

  Access from Kotlin:
    import rounds.libraries.resources.generated.resources.Res as AppRes
    import org.jetbrains.compose.resources.stringResource
    stringResource(AppRes.string.settings_title)

  For format args: stringResource(AppRes.string.key, arg1, arg2)
-->
