    <!-- Donation message copy (cycled) -->
    <string name="donation_positive">Throw me a coffee</string>
    <string name="donation_negative">Not today</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_01_title">No ads, no subs, no tracking.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_01_body">If that's the kind of thing you want more of on your phone, a few bucks helps me keep at it.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_02_title">I'm the only person making this.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_02_body">If this app has helped you, a coffee-sized tip would genuinely make my week.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_03_title">A donate popup in a HIIT app is tonally weird.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_03_body">I know. But this really is free, made by one guy, and there's really no other revenue. Help a stranger out?</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_04_title">No pressure.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_04_body">If you hate this app, close this. If you like it, there's a button. If you're indifferent, also close this.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_05_title">Shoutout to you, genuinely.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_05_body">You picked this over every free timer on the store. If you want to make that pick feel even better, the tip jar is open.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_06_title">Pretend this is a high five.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_06_body">You finished a workout. I finished an app. If you feel like sealing the deal with a tip, I would not hate it.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_07_title">Honest pitch:</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_07_body">I'd rather make this than almost anything else, but rent is still a thing. Tips help me keep picking this.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_08_title">Reminder that someone made this.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_08_body">Not a team. Not a company. Just a guy who wanted a HIIT timer that didn't suck. Buy him a coffee if you agree.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_09_title">Free forever is the plan.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_09_body">Tips are what keeps that plan viable. No guilt trip, just a heads up that the tip jar exists.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_10_title">You've done a few workouts in here now.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_10_body">If the app has earned a spot on your phone, maybe it's earned a couple bucks too.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_11_title">Tipping is optional.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_11_body">Everything else is too: no signup, no upsell, no nagging (well, except this one popup).</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_12_title">I don't know how to do this gracefully.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_12_body">So I'll just say it: if you can spare a few bucks, it means a lot. If you can't, no sweat. Carry on.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_13_title">Small brag:</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_13_body">This whole app was built by one person in their off hours. If that's the kind of thing you like supporting, now's the time.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_14_title">The tip jar is a real tip jar.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_14_body">Not a 'subscribe for features' trick. Pay nothing, pay something, same app either way.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_15_title">Sweaty hands, warm heart.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_15_body">You just finished a workout. While you're in a good mood, maybe consider tipping the dev. Maybe.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_16_title">Tips fund the next feature.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_16_body">And the one after that. And the bug fix I've been avoiding. All of it, honestly.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_17_title">Hey.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_17_body">If this app has been useful to you, a tip would be a genuinely nice thing to receive. Thanks for reading this far.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_18_title">Fair warning:</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_18_body">Clicking 'not today' will not make me sad. Clicking the other one will make me extremely un-sad.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_19_title">This app has no investors.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_19_body">Which means no one is telling me to add ads, upsells, or a paywall. Tips keep it that way.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_20_title">You showed up today.</string>
    <string name="donation_copy_20_body">Workouts are hard. Making an app is also kind of hard. If you want to reward the latter, the tip jar is open.</string>

